{"tid":1030722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秘魯酒店遇劫  約40名旅客被挾持包括中国香港人","createTime":"2019-02-21T06:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T10:39:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07eff891f245b905e787ab524716be426df51d56","tid":1030722,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"秘魯一間豪華酒店據報遇劫，約40名分別來自中國及美國的旅客被挾持，2人在事故中死亡。消息指出，旅客中有香港人。<br />\n<br />\n事發酒店位於東部馬德雷德迪奧斯地區，劫匪懷疑來自委內瑞拉及哥倫比亞。有英國傳媒報道，案發在當地星期二晚9時左右，遇劫的酒店位於亞馬遜偏遠地區。有秘魯傳媒引述內政部門說，警方已加緊行動，打擊可能由外國犯罪分子，組成的涉案犯罪集團。<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球網》引述中國駐秘魯使館消息指出，案發時有33名中國遊客入住酒店，目前他們安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB-%E7%B4%8440%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E6%9E%B6-060427925.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%2598%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%258A%25AB-%25E7%25B4%258440%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B6%2581%25E6%259E%25B6-060427925.html&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=a63e7ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB-%E7%B4%8440%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E6%9E%B6-060427925.html</a>"},{"pid":"5a351ccca563b3abc00def99c7639450828de4ab","tid":1030722,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812d735ba73a4dfe491af2884cc048833c462dee","tid":1030722,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-2